{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 150°C and line a large baking tray with baking paper.","Place a large bowl on mixing bowl lid, weigh in popcorn and set aside."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place honey, egg white and salt in mixing bowl then, without measuring cup, whisk <nobr>30 sec\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>.","Add almonds, pecans, cashews, Mexican spice, sesame seeds (if using) and cayenne then, without measuring cup, cook <nobr>5 min\/120°C\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add butter and cook <nobr>30 sec\/120°C\/\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Transfer nut mixture to bowl with reserved popcorn and toss with spatula to combine. Transfer to prepared baking tray and bake for 20 minutes (150°C), stirring after 10 minutes to ensure even baking. Do not overbake. Leave to cool before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["60 g salted popcorn (popped)","1 egg white, from large egg","30 g honey","¼ tsp fine sea salt, or to taste","120 g almonds, skin on","120 g pecan nuts","120 g cashew nuts","1 - 2 Tbsp Mexican spice mix, to taste","2 Tbsp sesame seeds              (optional)","½ tsp ground cayenne pepper, or to taste","30 g unsalted butter, diced"]}],"id":"r338898","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-Hve6Du3C-mo\/XZaq2IhSnoI\/AAAAAAAAhhk\/gHESyR5hZOoqDWrLSjcbmNAJ_vAAjj7kgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_q9a3yLAU8TdttZyA.png","title":"Spicy Nuts and Popcorn Mix","publishedAt":"2018-06-04T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8.6 g","fat":"29.6 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"17.5 g","calories":"1458 kJ \/ 348 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large baking tray, baking paper, large bowl, oven","basicInfo":["easy","10m","35m","8 portions"]}